        "Description": "The scientists working in Italy has made a request to kick Valeria out of their team, due to her arrogance and being useless to the research. We have no idea why there is a secret lab underground yet, but lets focus on the contract first. Good luck 47.\r\r在意大利工作的科学家们希望我们将Valeria踢出他们的队伍，因为她太过傲慢且对研究没有一点帮助。我们尚不清楚为何在地下会有这么一座秘密实验室，不过让我们先专注于完成契约吧。祝你好运47。",
